  <brief_title>Radiotherapy Followed by Adjuvant Chemotherapy in NK/T-cell Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Radiotherapy Followed by Chemotherapy With DICEP Regimen in Patients With NK/T-cell Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
